{"tid":501676,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【金仔發惡】倘美國打北韓 專家：重建費或達23.4萬億","createTime":"2017-12-17T06:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T06:50:23.000Z","uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"27701b709798b31f6fd7942cc8dd5902b73e3e55","tid":501676,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T06:00:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171216/57590745\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171216%2F57590745&d=AUk8h6ar0TC32KR9bgoZ5lKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=3f029d44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171216%2F57590745&h=82b425ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171216/57590745</a><br />\n<br />\n美國不排除以軍事選項作為對北韓的終極撒手鐧，但對北韓全面開戰要花多少錢？有智庫專家以伊拉克戰爭的8,150億美元（6.36萬億港元）軍費作參考，指對付規模更龐大的北韓軍隊，再加上戰後維穩和重建工作，軍費會是天文數字。<br />\n<br />\n華府智庫「焦點外交政策」（FPIF）主席費弗指，北韓軍隊人數是伊拉克當時的3倍，軍備亦更先進。而且，北韓情況跟當時的伊拉克相似，無論政權如何殘暴不仁，民眾同樣不會歡迎入侵的美國人，戰後恐須花長時間和巨額金錢維穩。<br />\n費弗指，即使美國在戰後能迅速平息亂局，軍事行動將造成災難性破壞，重建費用少則1萬億美元（7.8萬億港元），多則恐達3萬億美元（23.4萬億港元）。這樣的計算方法還未計戰事對全球經濟的影響，南韓經濟受創重勢將反噬美國。"},{"pid":"31d3e6dd453126ee342cf7024f8e12e6fadca95e","tid":501676,"uid":61105,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T06:03:02.000Z","msg":"建築商fat fat了"},{"pid":"73440b0f6076e14bbc91db556712595b663a4d12","tid":501676,"uid":26156,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T06:03:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b05868bd288219f4ad8e9072f18ed188036e4c3","tid":501676,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T06:04:24.000Z","msg":"高鐵總負債都冇咁多"},{"pid":"cda968de0804260ad9431a3dcac82faa06f42575","tid":501676,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T06:05:55.000Z","msg":"洗撚咩<br />\n打完咪算囉，重建咩"}